creator: Blue Ox Family Games, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Get ready for relaxing, word-building fun with the unique puzzles in 7 Little Words. Whether you enjoy word finds, anagram and jumble games, or crosswords, 7 Little Words is the perfect puzzle when you’re taking a short break or passing time while waiting!

Use the clues and letter blocks to find the scrambled words in each bite-size puzzle.

7 Little Words is FUN and EASY TO LEARN. We guarantee you've never played anything like it before. Give 7 Little Words a try today!

From the creators of Moxie - Word Traveler, Monkey Wrench, and Red Herring.
descriptionShort: Like word games? This fun twist on crossword puzzles is your daily brain warmup.
